node.name: Twist Top Bottle 330mL (test)
node.description: Carlton Dry is clean filtered for a refreshingly crisp, dry lager. Low in bitterness, it delivers superior drinkability from the first sip to the last.

node.name: The Dawdler Low Carb Lager Cans 375mL (test)
node.description: LARGO The Dawdler is a refreshing, easy-drinking lager for people who like to feel good about the choices they make. This low-carb beer is crisp and clean in more ways than one, Largo is committed to balancing its carbon footprint. Expect a slightly hazy appearance with light cereal malt notes and a crisp dry finish.

node.name: Pale Ale Bottles 375mL (test)
node.description: Coopers Pale Ale The Original Pale Ale. Beware of pale imitations. Guaranteed to turn heads, this is the beer that inspired a new generation of ale drinkers. With its fruity and floral characters, balanced with a crisp bitterness, Coopers Pale Ale has a compelling flavour which is perfect for every occasion.
